#Title
Search by city name and country

#Description
On the main page of application you can search city by its name and country

#Pre-conditions
The application is installed

#Steps
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Type 'Aalburg, NL' into search field
4. Wait until search result is loaded

#Expected result
At least one city is found
All displayed cities start with 'Aalburg, NL'